---
// src/components/SignalStack.astro
// No imports needed.
---

<section class="py-24 bg-slate-950 relative overflow-hidden" id="how-it-works">
    
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-full h-full max-w-7xl pointer-events-none">
        <div class="absolute top-40 left-20 w-96 h-96 bg-blue-900/20 rounded-full blur-[100px]"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-40 right-20 w-96 h-96 bg-purple-900/10 rounded-full blur-[100px]"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
        
        <div class="mb-16 md:text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            <h2 class="text-blue-400 font-bold tracking-widest text-xs uppercase mb-4">
                Proprietary Technology
            </h2>
            <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight mb-6">
                The Unfair Advantage System.
            </h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-lg">
                Three invisible technologies we build into your site to force Google to see you as the market leader.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            
            <div class="group relative p-8 bg-slate-900 rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 hover:border-blue-500/50 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-blue-900/20 transition-all duration-300">
                
                <div class="h-32 mb-6 bg-slate-950 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl overflow-hidden relative flex items-center justify-center">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-20" style="background-image: radial-gradient(#475569 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 10px 10px;"></div>
                    
                    <div class="relative w-full px-6 flex items-center justify-between">
                        <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2 relative z-10">
                            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-slate-800 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center border border-slate-600 text-slate-400">
                                <i data-lucide="user" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
                            </div>
                            <span class="text-[9px] font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wide">Customer</span>
                        </div>

                        <div class="flex-1 h-0.5 border-t-2 border-dashed border-blue-500/50 relative mx-2">
                             <div class="absolute -top-3 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 bg-blue-900/50 text-blue-300 text-[8px] font-bold px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-blue-500/30 whitespace-nowrap backdrop-blur-md">
                                SIGNAL PATH
                             </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2 relative z-10">
                            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center border-2 border-slate-900 shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(37,99,235,0.5)] text-white">
                                <i data-lucide="map-pin" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
                            </div>
                            <span class="text-[9px] font-bold text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-wide">You</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
                    <i data-lucide="map" class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500"></i>
                    GPS Handshake
                </h4>
                <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
                    Google usually ignores you if you aren't "next door." We code <strong>50+ Digital Pathways</strong> into your site, mathematically proving you serve specific neighborhoods miles away.
                </p>
                <div class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wide pt-4 border-t border-slate-800">
                    Result: Rank in 50+ Towns
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="group relative p-8 bg-slate-900 rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 hover:border-yellow-500/50 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-yellow-900/20 transition-all duration-300">
                
                <div class="h-32 mb-6 bg-slate-950 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl overflow-hidden relative flex items-center justify-center p-4 shadow-inner">
                    <div class="w-full max-w-[240px] space-y-2 opacity-90">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 mb-1.5">
                            <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-slate-700"></div>
                            <div class="h-1 w-16 bg-slate-700 rounded-full"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="h-2.5 w-full bg-blue-900/50 rounded-sm"></div>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-yellow-900/10 p-1.5 -ml-1.5 rounded border border-yellow-500/10">
                            <div class="flex gap-0.5">
                                <i data-lucide="star" class="w-3 h-3 text-yellow-500 fill-yellow-500"></i>
                                <i data-lucide="star" class="w-3 h-3 text-yellow-500 fill-yellow-500"></i>
                                <i data-lucide="star" class="w-3 h-3 text-yellow-500 fill-yellow-500"></i>
                                <i data-lucide="star" class="w-3 h-3 text-yellow-500 fill-yellow-500"></i>
                                <i data-lucide="star" class="w-3 h-3 text-yellow-500 fill-yellow-500"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class="h-1.5 w-8 bg-slate-700 rounded-full"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
                    <i data-lucide="star" class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-500 fill-yellow-500"></i>
                    Trust Beacon
                </h4>
                <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
                    We inject invisible code to force your 5-star rating to appear in Google Search results. Your link shines with yellow stars while competitors look plain.
                </p>
                <div class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wide pt-4 border-t border-slate-800">
                    Result: +30% Click Rate
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="group relative p-8 bg-slate-900 rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 hover:border-green-500/50 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-green-900/20 transition-all duration-300">
                
                <div class="h-32 mb-6 bg-slate-950 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl overflow-hidden relative flex flex-col justify-center items-center p-4">
                    
                    <div class="w-full space-y-3">
                        <div class="flex justify-between px-2 text-[9px] text-slate-600 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">
                            <span>Rank</span>
                            <span>Score</span>
                        </div>

                        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-green-900/10 border border-green-500/20 p-2 rounded-lg transform scale-105 shadow-lg relative z-10">
                            <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded bg-green-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold shadow-lg shadow-green-900/50">1</div>
                            <div class="flex-1">
                                <div class="h-1.5 w-16 bg-slate-200 rounded-full mb-1"></div>
                                <div class="h-1 w-8 bg-green-500/40 rounded-full"></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="text-green-400 text-xs font-bold">9.8</div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 px-2 opacity-30 grayscale">
                            <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded bg-slate-800 text-slate-500 flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border border-slate-700">2</div>
                            <div class="flex-1 h-1.5 w-12 bg-slate-700 rounded-full"></div>
                            <div class="text-slate-600 text-xs font-bold">7.4</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>

                <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
                    <i data-lucide="trophy" class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500"></i>
                    Comparison Winner
                </h4>
                <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
                    We build <strong>"Best Of" Review Pages</strong> that position you as the #1 Editor's Choice. We control the narrative before they call anyone else.
                </p>
                <div class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wide pt-4 border-t border-slate-800">
                    Result: Win The Research
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>

        <div class="mt-16 text-center">
            <a href="#pricing" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-blue-400 font-bold hover:text-blue-300 transition-colors">
                See which plan includes the System 
                <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
            </a>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>